```{r pancreas 32172219, include=FALSE}

PMID_32172219 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32172219', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32172219 <- paste0(PMID_32172219$journal,' ', PMID_32172219$year, ' ', PMID_32172219$month,';', PMID_32172219$volume,'(', PMID_32172219$number,'):', PMID_32172219$pages)

PubMed_32172219 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32172219$eprint)

doi_32172219 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32172219$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
